00:59:51.960 --> 00:59:54.361
Ubio si ga.
- Ubio si Venus Williams.

00:59:54.440 --> 00:59:57.108
Vratit će me natrag
u zatvor, Carl!

00:59:57.480 --> 01:00:00.165
Sranje.
- Cronut!

